""severity","category","resource","title","recommendation"
"high","api-version","PodSecurityPolicy/legacy-psp","Deprecated or removed API version","PodSecurityPolicy was removed; migrate to Pod Security Admission or a reviewed third-party admission webhook."
"high","api-version","PodSecurityPolicy/legacy-psp","PodSecurityPolicy is removed","Migrate to Pod Security Admission or a reviewed third-party admission webhook before relying on this policy in newer clusters."
"high","api-version","CronJob/nightly-legacy-sync (legacy)","Deprecated or removed API version","Update this manifest to a served API version before relying on a cluster upgrade. Migrate to batch/v1, available since v1.21."
"high","api-version","Ingress/legacy-web (legacy)","Deprecated or removed API version","Ingress v1 renames backend fields and requires pathType on each path. Migrate to networking.k8s.io/v1, available since v1.19."
"high","api-version","PodDisruptionBudget/legacy-web-pdb (legacy)","Deprecated or removed API version","policy/v1 changes empty selector behavior: {} selects all pods in the namespace. Migrate to policy/v1, available since v1.21."
"medium","reliability","CronJob/nightly-legacy-sync (legacy)","Missing resource limits","Add a memory limit and decide explicitly whether a CPU limit is appropriate for this workload. The example below is only a placeholder and must be tuned."
"medium","reliability","CronJob/nightly-legacy-sync (legacy)","Missing resource requests","Set CPU and memory requests for this container using measured usage as a starting point. The example below is a placeholder, not a universal production value."
"medium","security","CronJob/nightly-legacy-sync (legacy)","Missing seccomp profile","Set seccompProfile.type: RuntimeDefault unless the app has a reviewed need for a custom profile."
"medium","security","CronJob/nightly-legacy-sync (legacy)","runAsNonRoot should be true","Set runAsNonRoot: true at pod level when possible so every container inherits the safer default."
"medium","networking","Ingress/legacy-web (legacy)","Ingress does not configure TLS","Add a TLS block for the intended hosts and bind it to the certificate secret your ingress controller should use."
"medium","best-practice","Ingress/legacy-web (legacy)","Missing recommended app labels","Add the standard app.kubernetes.io labels with values that reflect the app name, instance, component, broader system, and deployment manager."
"low","security","CronJob/nightly-legacy-sync (legacy)","allowPrivilegeEscalation should be false","Set allowPrivilegeEscalation: false unless the application has a reviewed need for it."
"low","security","CronJob/nightly-legacy-sync (legacy)","Capabilities should drop ALL by default","Start from capabilities.drop: [""ALL""] and then add back only the minimum reviewed capabilities if the app truly requires them."
"low","security","CronJob/nightly-legacy-sync (legacy)","Container may run as root by default","Set runAsNonRoot: true explicitly and, when needed, choose a reviewed non-zero UID for the container."
"low","security","CronJob/nightly-legacy-sync (legacy)","readOnlyRootFilesystem should be true","Set readOnlyRootFilesystem: true if the app can run from mounted writable paths such as emptyDir, PVCs, or dedicated cache directories."
"low","operations","Ingress/legacy-web (legacy)","Missing owner or team metadata","Add a team label and owner annotation that match how your organization routes operational responsibility."
"low","operations","Service/legacy-web (legacy)","Missing owner or team metadata","Add a team label and owner annotation that match how your organization routes operational responsibility."
"low","best-practice","Service/legacy-web (legacy)","Missing recommended app labels","Add the standard app.kubernetes.io labels with values that reflect the app name, instance, component, broader system, and deployment manager.""
`;

